 <br>
It’s not perfect, but if I were in that situation (Matriarch), I’d let matters be until such a time as the Pride were more secure, until I had the resources to influence the men and the wherewithal to make a change in the leadership in the case of a ‘bad’ Alpha.  In short, they were in bad shape and did the best they could with the resources they had available.<br>
