<br>
Add to this that women are free from abandonment and do not have to be ‘single’ parents, they enjoy the benefits of the security a husband can provide and the benefits that a husband can provide in the area of defense.  All in all, a very nice deal for a woman if she wishes to reproduce.  She is safe, secure; she has the comfort of knowing she ahs a mate to help with the rearing of her children.  Since this system provides an answer to all of her concerns when it comes to mating, I would think there would be no desire to change her role either…. <br>
<br>
All In all while I know there is a treacherous side to these Nietzscheans, I also find them fascinating because they are in fact only being true to themselves.  Something I have taken to heart and in so doing learned a great deal about myself and the cultural limitations I have allowed to be placed upon myself.  Not a bad days work if you ask me.<br>
